>>65034303-eeb9-446f-8789-cf1c94b5825e
I'm guessing you're on Tor? Some anti-fingerprinting features have broken default Tor image posting. If you want to post images on Tor then you need to do:
>on Tor go to about:config in the address bar
>type resistfingerprinting
>set the following three options to false
>privacy.resistFingerprinting
>privacy.resistFingerprinting.autoDeclineNoUserInputCanvasPrompts
>services.sync.prefs.sync.privacy.resistFingerprinting
